{"tid":1627683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"知唔知點解今日被捕人數都咁少？","createTime":"2019-10-05T17:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T17:32:04.000Z","uid":315584,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7b0afa1c4965b1db295af18f353dd80be3969224","tid":1627683,"uid":315584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:10:23.000Z","msg":"首先係琴晚18區嘅黨鐵站都被破壞<br />\n<br />\n然後係因為黨鐵已經得返好少後備零件，冇可能可將18區嘅站都完全修復，所以佢地煩惱緊點樣修復個黨鐵站先係最好方法<br />\n<br />\n今朝個班吹風向嘅人好可能係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一大朝早，吹風向話要休息一日，但明明琴晚各位都玩得好開心，好夜先訓。同時，黨鐵又因爲零件不足而開唔返。眾所9知，黨鐵以家係運狗列車，黨鐵壞左，狗只能夠由地面運兵<br />\n<br />\n所以，原來黨鐵壞左佢地係會咁驚。各位千其唔好係黨鐵重開後又即刻入去拆佢站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會好影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />活動嫁嘛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">第一次開呢類post，可能講到1999，各位要屌請細力d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"9dea4e7597ec87d23216bfa0d8674efda7cf2d2b","tid":1627683,"uid":315584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:11:20.000Z","msg":"黨鐵已經有部分車站重開啦，你地千其唔好又打爆站入面d機啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81e7c68890e3bd83d80425e73a4e73009f4662ac","tid":1627683,"uid":5737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9dea4e7597ec87d23216bfa0d8674efda7cf2d2b","tid":1627683,"uid":315584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:11:20.000Z","msg":"黨鐵已經有部分車站重開啦，你地千其唔好又打爆站入面d機啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:12:21.000Z","msg":"有d鬼<br />\n我相信黨鐵會比一批狗入控制室 standby <br />\n唔會咁on9日日比我地扑<br />\n小心呀 手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/